^B@2^*BLaryy Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|Not really important. Rather than focus on the top honors, I care more about the intermediate spots. I'd much rather have Q J T 9 8 7 than A K 5 4 3 2. The cards in the middle are what make the suit of "good quality" for preempting.|
